# Project skills catalog

Include this rule when the user @mentions **`esoterica-skills`** or asks what skills exist. Skills are **opt-in**; see `skills-opt-in.mdc`.

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Ideation / exploration | `.cursor/skills/brainstorming/SKILL.md` |
| System design & trade-offs | `.cursor/skills/architecture/SKILL.md` (plus linked `.md` in that folder) |
| Linting & validation | `.cursor/skills/lint-and-validate/SKILL.md` (`scripts/` when relevant) |
| Frontend implementation | `.cursor/skills/frontend-developer/SKILL.md` |
| Visual craft | `.cursor/skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md` |
| Accessibility (WCAG) | `.cursor/skills/wcag-audit-patterns/SKILL.md`, `resources/implementation-playbook.md` |

To use one, @mention that skill or its path; do not assume skills apply without that.
